The paper deals with deep image synthesis, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of texture patches to control image synthesis also falls under graphics (cs.GR). The paper also mentions the use of generative networks, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper discusses the use of loss functions to train the generative network, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
